{"tid":1414861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家講咩連登仔都唔會聽入腦(入黎屌我)","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:32:26.000Z","uid":258067,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74fb300b99d4adcab728e8d84c9daebd9c880408","tid":1414861,"uid":258067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"隔離個post叫人唔好搞記律部隊宿舍，唔只黑警住喺裏面，啲人即刻話咩<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;有殺錯無放過&quot;&quot;唔好怨我哋，怨黑警&quot;.</span> 又有個post話冇目的咁放火觀感唔係咁好，和理非屋企人好反感，啲人又即刻話<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;如果你見到尋日天水圍少女個事都覺得放火有問題嘅話請你去死&quot;</span>. 勇武係冇問題，但係唔好<span style=\"color: red;\">將抗爭嘅手段當係目的</span>, 成日講話如果你同我一樣咁嬲就唔會覺得有問題，乜原來覺得嬲就可以做乜都得？咁你啲黑警有咩分別？一路以黎我哋都係受市民支持係因為我地有道德高地高地呀。合理勇武係絕對冇問題架。你打斷晒啲黑警嘅手手腳腳我都唔會出一句聲，但係喺做之前唔該諗吓你嘅行動對場運動<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇幫助</span>而唔係由情緒主導。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運亨通</span></span>"},{"pid":"1fa77946f1cd3ef68e704fd9f9fc18f3d4e360b1","tid":1414861,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"70ab7edeefaa8630e8317df33ea4fee3c1c3b509","tid":1414861,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6273bc1e9c969cf2281daf0766f3e921ff72688f","tid":1414861,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"934e4c772bd35af15caacc922168922b709729d0","tid":1414861,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e3cde4c6082b1573040d4ed3fa724f56e9d5716a","tid":1414861,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"挑戰十連"},{"pid":"ade6c44ee26db96efd83eca6e097304eaab7142f","tid":1414861,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2314d0736c2bc5c636937255a5a6dd2fd26a4989","t